Real features for Hoogoord 131:
- lots of natural daylight;
- well maintained 4-room apartment;
- near the shopping center Amsterdamse Poort;
- good accessibility, by public transport and car;
- green living environment;

Is Hoogoord 131 really what you are looking for?
In combination with the pictures below we give you a brief impression of the apartment.

Bright and well maintained 4-room apartment with balcony free view, located on the 9th floor with storage in the basement. The apartment is located in the Zuidoost district. Centrally located with around the corner shopping center Amsterdamse Poort with stores and interspersed with small specialty stores. You can go there for daily shopping, delicious lunches and unique products from local entrepreneurs. Train and subway station Bijlmer Arena is within walking distance of the complex and you can reach Amsterdam Central Station in about 15 minutes. By bike you can reach the city center in about 25 minutes. There is plenty of greenery in the area including: the Nelson Mandela Park, Bijlmerwijde and the Gaasperpark where you can swim in the Gaasperplas! The whole is well maintained with double glazing, heating by district heating, parquet floor, modern fitted kitchen and bathroom. During a viewing you can see the atmosphere and space of the apartment.

